Class btManifoldPoint

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.bytedeco.javacpp.Pointer
      • org.bytedeco.bullet.BulletCollision.btManifoldPoint
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    AutoCloseable

    @NoOffset
 @Properties(inherit=BulletCollision.class)
public class btManifoldPoint
extends Pointer
    ManifoldContactPoint collects and maintains persistent contactpoints. used to improve stability and performance of rigidbody dynamics response.
